{"tid":1550342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十月一日","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T03:44:07.000Z","uid":216995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11a858259983f413e48e624096dc3b5449882d3b","tid":1550342,"uid":216995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"大家都話十月一日國慶要好好賀佢，究竟係點賀？<br />\n<br />\n個人推薦起碼嚟個真。戒嚴。<br />\n雖然而家班popo搞到同戒嚴無咩分別。但係政府死都唔肯宣布<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以究竟點先可以實現到？<br />\n求指點。"},{"pid":"87d2c2cb6dea986d57a1fbbdef8f0c9ba6c481a6","tid":1550342,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28707307739f5b5e803613f2acf6a05136f21d74","tid":1550342,"uid":216995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:41:47.000Z","msg":"Pish!"},{"pid":"85194cb0c3e3e4e891e6f53e20f48405164ed447","tid":1550342,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"全部唔出街、唔消費得唔得？"},{"pid":"20c4c19721d174eca65f33d8fe7829411d5d7a10","tid":1550342,"uid":216995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85194cb0c3e3e4e891e6f53e20f48405164ed447","tid":1550342,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"全部唔出街、唔消費得唔得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲係自我戒嚴，同埋咁大班港豬，邊可能唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32a97db7efec6c002da5d40a1751417a2e19dcc","tid":1550342,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"有巴打講過，拎晒全世界嘅國旗出街fing，唯獨冇支那旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1db42413c83854d7642f157a903b4a2300a82c","tid":1550342,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"一定要落中共面<br />\n今年70週年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a89a599f4b0c6895bbf4ab456b836b4258affe","tid":1550342,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e32a97db7efec6c002da5d40a1751417a2e19dcc","tid":1550342,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"有巴打講過，拎晒全世界嘅國旗出街fing，唯獨冇支那旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:57:57.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打講個唱美國國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d653735953b8d3ce561c317ed2daf69b0a06b959","tid":1550342,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21a89a599f4b0c6895bbf4ab456b836b4258affe","tid":1550342,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e32a97db7efec6c002da5d40a1751417a2e19dcc","tid":1550342,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"有巴打講過，拎晒全世界嘅國旗出街fing，唯獨冇支那旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:57:57.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打講個唱美國國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h